This example will solve a Possion equation on a gmsh generated data. 
The obtained solution is saved in file "u.dx".

Usage:
	1. compile with make [-e debug=no];
	2. generate the mesh with gmsh as:
	     $ gmsh -3 Cube.geo
	     $ gmsh2mesh Cube.msh Cube.mesh
	     $ mesh_refine 3 Cube.mesh Cube3.mesh 3 0
	3. run with ./run.sh Cube3.mesh;
	4. view the obtained numerical solution with OpenDX;

